    <briefdescription>
<para>Helper struct to test convertibility. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Contains two test functions:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ref refid="structDali_1_1Detail_1_1ConvertibleHelper_1a1bcfde715be2cc5dc5a51c869b7ea2dd" kindref="member">Test(From)</ref>: Accepts the source type and returns the target type</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="structDali_1_1Detail_1_1ConvertibleHelper_1a38fcf2426366a4a357c0d8f8382e966d" kindref="member">Test(AnyType)</ref>: Accepts anything via the <ref refid="structDali_1_1Detail_1_1AnyType" kindref="compound">AnyType</ref> constructor and returns char</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>The compiler will select the best match based on overload resolution, which allows us to detect implicit convertibility. </para>
